00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:17,460

2
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:22,560
 'Pursue Love' - Chen Zhuo Xuan

3
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:27,840
♫  Don't be afraid, no matter how long the journey  ♫

4
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:34,980
♫  Love embraces gentleness and care  ♫

5
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:41,520
♫  Those scars will eventually heal and turn into the blossoms gathering along time's journey  ♫

6
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:49,280
♫  Eventually, someone will take them away for you  ♫

7
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:52,620
♫  Don't feel lonely moving on  ♫

8
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:56,040
♫  Let time in on your story  ♫

9
00:00:56,040 --> 00:01:03,100
♫  Expect a soft ray of light in response  ♫

10
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:06,680
♫  May you find her admist the crowd  ♫

11
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:10,260
♫  May you find joy in simplicity  ♫

12
00:01:10,260 --> 00:01:17,360
♫  Even though you know life is filled with regrets  ♫

13
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:23,800
♫  May you always carry your passion every Winter and Summer  ♫

14
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:26,060

15
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:31,060

16
00:01:31,060 --> 00:01:34,540
It's all good. You can get up now.

17
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:42,180
Wei'an, I really want to hold you like this every day.

18
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:48,940
The medical aid program is over, the hospital wants me to come back.

19
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:52,560
The medical aid program is over, the hospital wants me to come back.

20
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:01,500
But I'll apply for an extension.

21
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,300
In any case,

22
00:02:03,940 --> 00:02:06,780
I'll be wherever you are.

23
00:02:25,060 --> 00:02:26,790
Where are you going?

24
00:02:27,380 --> 00:02:29,560
To watch the sunrise.

25
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:32,840
Are you angry?

26
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,620
Actually,

27
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:39,940
the assistance mission won't have any impact on me.

28
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:43,340
As long as I apply with the hospital, they'll definitely agree.

29
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:45,300
I'm not angry.

30
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:48,740
And you don't have to make any changes for me.

31
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:50,780
I don't have any plans.

32
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:53,440
I always go wherever life takes me.

33
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:57,780
I don't even know where I'm going next month.

34
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,360
Then...

35
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:05,360
I'll follow you wherever you go.

36
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:10,260
I just want to be with you forever.

37
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,360
Is that okay?

38
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:34,020
It's so beautiful.

39
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:40,140
Wei'an.

40
00:03:41,780 --> 00:03:48,060
For the rest of my life, I hope to watch every sunrise with you.

41
00:04:12,740 --> 00:04:17,640
 Then, I'll follow you wherever you go.

42
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:21,300
 I just want to be with you forever.

43
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:25,080
 Gu Yunzheng, I have no regrets anymore.

44
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:27,440
 I'm afraid to ask for more.

45
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,160
 How long is forever?

46
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:32,800
 I can't think about things that are too far ahead.

47
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:39,020
Wei'an, if you're tired, you can rest.

48
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:49,840

49
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:52,800
 I may not...

50
00:04:54,480 --> 00:05:01,140
 I'm afraid I won't be able to attend your 80th birthday anymore. But I'll send you your gift on time.

51
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:03,920
 Why so sudden?

52
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:07,160
 Do you have a girlfriend?

53
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:14,020
Yes, we just started dating.

54
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:18,100
 We're still getting to know each other, so I want to stay here for now.

55
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:22,660
No problem, you can stay there as long as you'd like.

56
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,600
 I will always support you.

57
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:29,920
 I’m thinking, if you're already in love, I have to start preparing too.

58
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,840
 Which house should become your newlywed home?

59
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:35,170
 It'll need to be renovated.

60
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:38,940
Grandpa, aren't you being too anxious?

61
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:40,380
It's too early for that.

62
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:41,980
 Sure, no problem.

63
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:48,040
 Yunzheng, remember, no matter what you decide, I will always support you.

64
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,080
Got it.

65
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:54,200
All right, Grandpa, I'm going to hang up and go do my rounds now.

66
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,940
Newlywed home?

67
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,720
Boss.

68
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:05,540
I'm going to go do my rounds. Please step aside.

69
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:14,130
Stand still.

70
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:24,040
What's going on?

71
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:27,180
His foot healed in one night.

72
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:29,060
And he's going crazy.

73
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:30,400
Interpreter Su really is amazing.

74
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:33,400

75
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:59,920
Boss, you're not only good with scalpels, but also with decorating knives.

76
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,680
When did you learn such a skill?

77
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:13,800
 Sweetie, do you like the birthday cake I bought you?

78
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:18,300
 Yes. I also want a toy car that's this big.

79
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:21,960
 Okay, I will buy you whatever you want.

80
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,630
 Zheng Zheng!

81
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:47,820
 - Grandpa. 
 - Zheng Zheng, you're back.

82
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:50,080
 Zheng Zheng, put your backpack down and close your eyes.

83
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:52,540
 I have a surprise for you.

84
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,720
 Close your eyes.

85
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,500
 Wait a minute.

86
00:08:09,220 --> 00:08:12,450
♪  Happy birthday to you  ♪

87
00:08:12,450 --> 00:08:19,030
♪  Happy birthday to you  ♪

88
00:08:19,030 --> 00:08:23,800
♪  Happy birthday to you  ♪

89
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:26,020
 - Do you like this cake? 
 - Yes.

90
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:29,200
 Grandpa, how did you know I like car-shaped cakes?

91
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,000
 I asked the employee at the cake shop.

92
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:35,560
 They said that kids like this kind of car-shaped cake. Is that right?

93
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:37,360
 Come here.

94
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:40,340
 Let's close our eyes and make a wish now.

95
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:46,560
 I hope I can see Mom again.

96
00:08:49,815 --> 00:08:53,680
 - Okay. Let's start blowing out the candles now, okay? 
 - Okay.

97
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:57,520
 Come on. One, two, three.

98
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:02,120
 Great! Our Zheng Zheng is another year older.

99
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:05,540
 - Let's eat the cake! 
 - Okay.

100
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:07,840
 Zheng Zheng.

101
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,940
 Grandpa, you eat it first.

102
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,440
 It's so delicious. Here.

103
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,340
 Is it good?

104
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:31,720
 I feel a little dizzy.

105
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:36,800
 What did I tell you? Grandpa has diabetes and can't eat cake.

106
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,980
 You still made him eat so much?

107
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:43,160
 He's just a child.

108
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,800
 Usually, his mom doesn't discipline him much.

109
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:47,500
 He can be selfish and willful.

110
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:49,380
 Stop.

111
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:52,000
 You're making a fuss.

112
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,940
 I love cake myself.

113
00:09:54,940 --> 00:09:57,000
 It has nothing to do with Zheng Zheng.

114
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,840
 Dad, you have ketoacidosis now.

115
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,600
 And you're still explaining for him?

116
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:04,940
 Don’t you know how serious the complications are?

117
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:06,220
 He's right, Dad.

118
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:08,660
 You can't spoil kids like this.

119
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:10,200
 Spoiling a child is like killing him.

120
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:16,980
 I can pamper my own grandson as much as I want.

121
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:23,360
 Grandpa, are you feeling better now?

122
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:26,700
 I'm sorry, it's all my fault.

123
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:30,380
 I’m fine. I'm just getting old.

124
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:34,760
 It's normal to have some physical problems.

125
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:37,280
 It has nothing to do with you.

126
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:40,780
 Grandpa, actually, I don't like birthday cakes.

127
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:44,160
 I won't eat birthday cakes anymore.

128
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:58,630

129
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,820
 It's so beautiful.

130
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:09,360
 It must be for someone important, right?

131
00:11:10,410 --> 00:11:13,590

132
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:27,820
 Sir, are you not going to take your cake?

133
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:34,020
 I don't have anyone to share it with.

134
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:36,840
 Split it with your staff and customers.

135
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:48,680

136
00:11:56,360 --> 00:12:02,920
 Mom, I finally found someone to share birthday cakes with.

137
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:08,460

138
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:11,380

139
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:14,280
What did you say? What did you just say?

140
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:16,160
Gu Yunzheng isn't going back anymore?

141
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,080
Why are you so excited?

142
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:19,320
How can I not be excited?

143
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:23,020
I originally wanted to use Gu Yunzheng's beauty trap to trick you back home.

144
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:25,000
Who knew he would stay too now?

145
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:28,460
I'm throwing meat at a dog who never comes back.

146
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:31,120
Who's the meat and dog?

147
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,720
You.

148
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,160
My God.

149
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:37,880
My plans are all ruined.

150
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:43,500
I matched you two because I wanted you to go back together, not stay in Lakaya.

151
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:46,817
Aren't you also tied to someone in Lakaya?

152
00:12:46,817 --> 00:12:48,737
And you're still telling me off.

153
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:59,220
Wei'an, but I'm still very happy for you.

154
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:01,200
You're finally in love.

155
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:03,800
And Dr. Gu is such a good person.

156
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,960
With him around, he can take care of you and love you.

157
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,940
I'm also relieved.

158
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:15,240
Tell me, what did you two do that night in the desert?

159
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:18,220
You want to know?

160
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,220
I'm not telling you.

161
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:29,180
Su Wei'an, how could you do this to me? You heartless person.

162
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:32,020
I've never hidden my love experiences from you.

163
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:34,360
Why won't you tell me when it's your turn?

164
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,920
I'm not keeping it from you.

165
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:39,720
It's just that we don't have that kind of relationship yet.

166
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:42,920
That stupid Gu Yunzheng hasn't confessed to you yet?

167
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:44,720
It's not that.

168
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:51,460
He... He confessed already.

169
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:54,100
It's just that I haven’t thought it through yet.

170
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:56,520
Isn't he the man of your dreams?

171
00:13:57,840 --> 00:14:01,840
Let me tell you, you won't find anyone else this good if you pass on him.

172
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:04,120
What are you still hesitating about?

173
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:08,280
What's the matter with you?

174
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:12,400
You've got the man of your dreams, and you're still acting cool with me here.

175
00:14:16,350 --> 00:14:19,800
It's okay. You don't have to consider my feelings.

176
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:22,120
Just laugh if you want to.

177
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,380
I know you want to laugh.

178
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:30,200
He told me he wanted to be with me forever,

179
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:33,120
but I'm not sure...

180
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,760
if I can keep this promise.

181
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:45,220
Su Wei'an, are you humble bragging to me?

182
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,320
I'm really speechless.

183
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:51,620
Gu Yunzheng told you that he wanted to be with you forever, but you're still not happy.

184
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:54,800
If it were me, I would marry him immediately.

185
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,460
- Who's that? 
 - Sister Lan.

186
00:14:57,680 --> 00:14:59,220
Really?

187
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:03,480
Hello, Sister Lan, why are you still awake?

188
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:07,560
 An An, your aunt is sick.

189
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:13,800
 She went to the hospital, and the doctor said she has something called chorea.

190
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:20,300
 The doctor also said that this disease is hereditary.

191
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:21,640
Anyway, I didn't really understand.

192
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:25,800
He also said that he didn’t know why it came up early.

193
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,620
 This disease is inherited from the second generation of the paternal line.

194
00:15:34,620 --> 00:15:36,880
 It could start around the age of 30.

195
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,900
 And the disease will be more serious.

196
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:42,440
 It'll start at the age of 30?

197
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:44,280
 Most likely.

198
00:15:49,280 --> 00:15:52,720
 Hello, An An, did you hear me?

199
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,560
 I don't know if you have time.

200
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:57,420
 Can you come back?

201
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:02,860
 Do you plan to stay in Lakaya forever?

202
00:16:02,860 --> 00:16:06,680
 I beg you, clear your head a bit.

203
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:08,360
 What about your research project?

204
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:11,880
 After years of hard work, can you just give up if you say so?

205
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:14,120
 Don't you care about Huaren's future?

206
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:16,400
 Think about it, why did you want to study medicine in the first place?

207
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:22,040
I studied medicine to treat illnesses and save people, not to write papers and get promoted.

208
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:25,042
I can treat people and save lives in Lakaya too.

209
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:30,229
Anyway, I've made up my mind to stay in Lakaya.

210
00:16:30,229 --> 00:16:32,149
You can't stop me.

211
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:58,160
You're back.

212
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:03,400
Wei'an, what are you doing? Where are you going?

213
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,080
I'm going back home.

214
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,240
Back home? No, wait.

215
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:11,040
Why? Didn't you just get together with Gu Yunzheng?

216
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,360
I've been thinking about it.

217
00:17:14,360 --> 00:17:17,560
I don't think I’m suitable for dating, making money is more important.

218
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:20,400
Su Wei'an, are you trying to lie to me again?

219
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,860
I really want to break up with you.

220
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:30,560
Wei'an, did something happen just now?

221
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:33,040
Did something happen to Sister Lan?

222
00:17:33,040 --> 00:17:34,260
No.

223
00:17:34,260 --> 00:17:37,480
Su Wei'an, how can you not keep your word?

224
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,960
Last time, you promised not to hide anything from me anymore.

225
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,900
What are you doing?

226
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:59,560
Jiang Jiang, my aunt has a rare disease.

227
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:02,180
I have to go back right away.

228
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:05,080
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

229
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:07,660
I don't want anyone to worry about me.

230
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:13,200
Is it... Huntington's disease?

231
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:15,120
How do you know?

232
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:21,960
The day you were stabbed and hospitalized,

233
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:27,500
Dr. Gu searched your bag and gave you a full physical exam.

234
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:31,100
He wouldn't have done that if he didn't suspect that you had some serious illness.

235
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:35,900
So I couldn't help but worry, and I searched your bag.

236
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:41,720
I found the genetic test report hidden in your notebook.

237
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:46,160
Don't worry. Gu Yunzheng didn't see it.

238
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:55,110
Wei'an, that's why you dropped out of school,

239
00:18:55,110 --> 00:19:00,140
risked your life to make money, researched euthanasia, and rejected Gu Yunzheng.

240
00:19:00,140 --> 00:19:02,100
It's all because of...

241
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:05,220
this chorea.

242
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:11,440
Please keep it a secret for me.

243
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:16,340
Don't tell anyone, especially Gu Yunzheng.

244
00:19:18,540 --> 00:19:20,240
Can you do that for me?

245
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:24,280
Wei'an, I don't think it's possible.

246
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:28,540
Is it possible that there was a mistake in the genetic test report?

247
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:31,140
I also hope it's a mistake.

248
00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:42,340
I thought that as long as I was braver, God would cut me some slack.

249
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:48,740
And let me fall in love without any regrets, and allow me to  have more time with Gu Yunzheng.

250
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:55,920
But now Auntie is sick.

251
00:19:58,140 --> 00:20:03,520
If I get sick, I'll get worse earlier than my aunt.

252
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:10,120
The future that Gu Yunzheng wants...

253
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:13,720
I can't give it to him.

254
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:20,120
Wei'an, don't say any more.

255
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:28,900
Why is God so unfair?

256
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:31,320
Why does it have to be you?

257
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,280
Okay.

258
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:37,760
It's okay.

259
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:41,000
Wei'an.

260
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:44,760
