00:32:58,340 --> 00:32:59,960
 I checked the surveillance carefully.

405
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:04,740
 Even though it's very slight, you can see my dad struggling.

406
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:07,320
 And his body seemed to be out of control.

407
00:33:08,560 --> 00:33:11,760
 Was there anything clearly abnormal about your father recently?

408
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:14,180
 Clearly abnormal.

409
00:33:14,180 --> 00:33:17,000
 Anything abnormal in the past three months.

410
00:33:18,220 --> 00:33:21,360
 He was under a lot of pressure and lost his temper easily. Do these count?

411
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:22,980
 Anything else?

412
00:33:22,980 --> 00:33:26,000
 He also fell easily on flat ground.

