00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:35,760
 Your father's abnormalities could very much be due to a neurological disease.

414
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:42,220
 If you want to know the reason, I suggest you go do a genetic test.

415
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:50,480
 Your genetic report shows that

416
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:54,580
 the number of repeat sequences of cytosine adenine and guanine trinucleotide in the IT15 gene is greater than 40,

417
00:33:54,580 --> 00:33:56,140
 which is beyond normal range.

418
00:33:56,140 --> 00:33:58,460
 You carry the gene that causes chorea.

419
00:33:58,460 --> 00:34:02,540
 If the disease occurs later on, you may lose control of your limbs.

